          4/05/20 12:00PM EST
        </Typography>
        <Typography className={classes.pos} color="textSecondary">
          Genre: Game Theory
        </Typography>
        <Typography variant="h5" component="h2" style={{textDecorationLine: 'underline'}}>
            Risk-Averse Equilibrium Analysis and Computation
